.TH RRSERVE @MAN_SECTION@ "@BUILD_DATE@"
.SH NAME
rrserve \- server application for multi-player ricochet robots game
.SH SYNOPSIS
rrserve --host <hostname> --port <port> --name <username> --game
<gamename> --watch
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
\fIRrserve\fP is a
server for the Ricochet Robots protocol. It provides for multiple
users to connect to multiple active games.
.SH USAGE
.PP
Options are as follows:
.TP
.B "--help,--usage"
Print a help/usage message and exit.
.TP
.BI "-l,--logfile " filename
Select a file to log all server messages to. By default, messages are
sent to stderr.
.TP
.BI "-p,--port " port
Select the TCP port to listen on. By default, rrserve listens on
port 5252.
